tafsir[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Saad: yewtere yawtiino, fii sugu …óee karfe ta∆¥ondir…óe, ka fu…ó…óorde simoore Baqarah. E ngol cortewol …óoo, Allah no woodanira Alqur'aana, yowondirnde e waajitor…ói yim…ìe, kon ko nafata …ìe aduna e laakara. Hara wanaa ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen aa∆¥otoo, wonnde Allah no mai denndadiijo."
  38,2,"Ko woni kon, heefer…ìe …ìen wonii e townitanagol wootin…óinnde Allah, e luutondirgol e Muhammadu (yo o his), e anygol mo."
  38,3,"∆äuu…óii e mofte fennu…ìe Nulaa…ìe mun, ado ma…ì…ìe, …ìe Men halki, …ìen noddi faaboo uma, nde lepte tellato, kono oon waqtu wonaana waqtu faabeede e lepte sakko faabo nafa …ìe."
  38,4,"∆Åe ≈ãal…ói, tuma …ìe yi'unoo Nulaa…óo ar…óo …ìe on, ko jertina …ìe e lepte Allah …óen, ko e ma…ì…ìe o jeyaa. Yeddu…ìe …ìen nde yi'unoo hujjaaji …ìanngin…ói goonga Muhammadu kan, …ìe wi'i: Oo, ko biloowo yim…ìe nii, heewu…óo fenaande e ko wi'ata kon, wonnde ko o Nulaa…óo, mo Allah wahayini e mun."
  38,5,"Kere o wa…óay rewetee…ói limtilimti…ói e mun …óin fow, rewetee…óo gooto tun? Pellet, ko huunde ha…ótirnde haawnagol non."
  38,6,"Mbatu ma…ì…ìe ngun hucciti, …ìe wi'ani yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen: Yehee, jokkon haaju mun, wata on naatu e diina Muhammadu, tabitee e rewetee…ói mon …óin. Anndon ko Muhammadu noddi on e mun kon, wiide yo on rewu gooto tun, ko ko o e…ì…ìani, fii no o waawira'en, wa…óten jokkude mo."
  38,7,"Men nanaali fii ko Muhammadu noddata men e mun kon, woni bajjin…óingol Allah ngol, e diina baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen, wanaa e diina Iisaa kan. Ko men naniri mo kon wonaali, si wanaa fenaande fefindaande."
  38,8,"Kere ko e makko Alqur'aana jippintee hakkunde amen, o heertora …óum e hoore amen, menen koohoo…ìe …ìen? Si ko woni, …ìee sirkoo…ìe wonii e sikkitagol wayahu mo mi jippini e maa…óa on. Fotde …ìe mee…óaali lepte Allah …óen, kono hi…ìe …óayintora nennitaneede …ìe. Si …ìe mee…óuno lepte …óen, …ìe ha…ì…ìitotanooko e yeddugol sirkana Allah, sikkitoo e ko O wahayini kon e maa…óa."
  38,9,"Kaa …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennoo…ìe jogiti ngaluuji …ìure Joomi maa, Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake On, Okkoowo mo O muuyani ye…óude. Wano ngalu ngu O ye…óirta Annabaaku, on mo O muuyani. Tawde wanaa kam…ìe …óum wonani, sakko …ìe ye…óa mo …ìe yi…óani, maa …ìe …óala go…ó…óo goo."
  38,10,"Kaa ko kam…ìe woodani laamagol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji? Sakko …ìe he…ìa feere ye…óugol e …óawugol! Si ko non …ìe aa∆¥ori, haray yo …ìe ∆¥een≈ãir kala sabu no …ìe hewtiryta ka kammuuli, fii no …ìe √±aawira ko …ìe yi…ói, woni ye…óugol maa …óalugol. Kono …ìe hippataa …óum!"
  38,11,"∆Åee fennoo…ìe Muhammadu jom kisiyee on, ko konu hoyngu, fooliroyteengu wano …óiya feddeeji fennunoo…ói Nulaa…ìe mun, ado ma…ì…ìe."
  38,12,"Wanaa …ìee woni ko adii fennude. Wo…ó…ìe adinoke …ìe e …óum, woni Yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen, e Aadi'en e Fir'awna lettiraynoo…óo yim…ìe …ìen, pempe."
  38,13,"Samuuda'en kadi, e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen, e yim…ìe Shu'aybu …ìen fow kadi fenni Nulaa…ìe mun …ìen. Ko …ìen woni feddeeji hawrunoo…ói e fennugol yedda ko Nulaa…ìe lun addannoo…ìe."
  38,14,"Alaa e …óin feddeeji, mo fennaali Nulaa…ìe …ìen. Lepte Allah …óen jojji e ma…ì…ìe, fii kala …óe tonngino haa e dumunna."
  38,15,"∆Åee fennoo…ìe Muhammadu (yo o his) habbaaki, si wanaa wuttaandu …ói…óa…ìuru ndun ka alaandu, ndu alaa ruttorde. Lepte …óen yana e ma…ì…ìe, si …ìe …ìe tuubaali ko adii."
  38,16,"∆Åe woni e jalkitugol wi'a: Joomi amen, yaccinan men ge…ìal lepte amen …óen aduna, ado √ëalaande Darngal."
  38,17,"An Nulaa…óo, mu√±√±o e ko fennoo…ìe …ìen wowlata maa kon; annditaa jeyaa…óo Amen on, Daawuuda, jom cemmbe dartor…óe ay…ìe mun, mu√±√±oo e …óoftagol Allah. Kanko ko o …óuu…óunoo…óo ruttoragol tuubannde Allah, e gollugol ko welata Mo."
  38,18,"Men elti pelle …óen, ko subbunhinoda e Daawuuda, ka kiikii…óe e ka weetugol."
  38,19,"Men elti kadi colli …óin, ka …ói moo…ìindiraa ka weeyo, tawi …ói fow majji, hi…óo …óoftanii subbunhinanagol Allah."
  38,20,"Men semmbiniri fii laamu Makko ngun, mirin mo Men okki mo on, wonndude e waawugol foola ay…ìe makko …ìen. Men ye…ói mo Annabaaku, e hawrugol e sawaaba. Men ye…ói Mo …óemngal laa…ìungal."
  38,21,"An Nulaa…óo, hara kabaaru wenjunoo…ìe …ìen …ói…óo arii maa, tuma nde …ìe ∆¥awunoo ka ganngunal Annabi Daawuuda nokku dewirdo mum!"
  38,22,"Tuma nde …ìe naatirnoo e juhal, ka Daawuuda, o …óe∆¥ii …ìe. ∆Åe anndi o …óen∆¥ike, …ìe wi'ani mo: wata a hulu ! Ko men yeddondir…ìe …ói…óo; go…ó…óo e amen too√±ii oya. Ko yo a √±aawir nun…óal hakkunde amen, wata a too√±u, tinndinaa men e laawol focciingol ngol, woni laawol sawaaba gol."
  38,23,"Gooto e ma…ì…ìe wi'iani Daawuuda: Oo gorko, ko musi…ó…óo am: himo jogii baalii cappan…óe jeenay e jeenay, min mi…óo jogii baalii gootii. O …óa…ì…ìiri lam henndingol mo ngil, o fooli lam e yewtere."
  38,24,"Daawuuda √±aawiri hakkunde ma…ì…ìe wi'angol wullitii…óo on: Pellet, musi…ó…óo maa on too√±irii ma, …óa…ì…ìugol …ìeydiyude baalii maa ngii, ka baali makko. Ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e hawtu…ìe, hino too√±indira hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa gom…óim…ìe golloo…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ói yamiraa…ói …óin; …ìen …óon, ko nun…óu…ìe hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, kono …ìe …óuu…óaa. Annabi Daawuuda felliti, wonnde Men jarriborii mo ngol wennjondiro. O …óa…ì…ìiri Joomi makko haforaneede, o suuyiri sujjugol, o tuubani Allah."
  38,25,"Men ja…ìirani mo tuubuubuyee, yaafanagol mo …óum. Pellet non, hino woodani ka Amen, …ìadal e mo∆¥∆¥ugol ruttorde laakara."
  38,26,"Ko an yo Daawuuda, Men wa…óii ma lomto ka hoore leydi. Siinu fiyakuuji diina e aduna …óin, √±aawiraa nun…óal hakkunde yim…ìe …ìen. Wata a jokku mbelee…óe, tuma √±aawataa hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, sakko too√±ataa go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe, sabu tawde oya on no …ìa…ói maa e jeya maa e weldigal, o majjiniri …óum, laawol Allah focciingol ngol. Anndaa, pellet, majjoo…ìe …ìen e ngol Allah focciingol, hino woodani …ìe lepte sa…ótu…óe, sabu ko …ìe yejjitiri kon, √ëalaande hasboore nden. Tawde si …ìe annditayno fii mayre, …ìe hula nde, …ìe jokkataano mbelee…óe."
  38,27,"Men tagiraali kammu ngun e leydi ndin meere. ∆äum ko sikke yeddu…ìe …ìen. Bone Yiite woodanii …ìen yeddu…ìe, sikku…ìe …óum, √ëalnde Darngal, si …ìe luttii e keeferaaku sikkitagol Allah ko boni !"
  38,28,"Men wa…óataa …ìen gom…óim…ìe Allah …ìe jokki Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, wano …ìen bonniroo…ìe ka leydi, geddi e keeferaaku. Men wa…óataa kadi hulir…ìe Joomi mun …ìen, …óoftagol yamirooje Makko, wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko, wano heefer…ìe …ìen e naafiqii…ìe yoolii…ìe e geddi …ìen. Fonnugol …ìe, ko oo√±aare nde yahdaa e Allah toowu…óo senii…óo On. Si ko woni, O yo…ìitiray gom…óim…ìe …ìen, naatugol Aljanna, O leptira yeddu…ìe …ìen, naatugol Yiite. Tawde …ìe fotataa ka Allah. Njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe kadi fotataa ka Makko."
  38,29,"Ko Deftere heewunde barki e nafa, woni ndee Alqur'aanaare, nde Men jippini e maa…óa. Fii no yim…ìe …ìen taskra miijitoo maanaaji mayre, joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen hisu…óe …ìen, waajitora."
  38,30,"Men ye…ói Daawuuda, ge…óal makko Sulaymaana, neema e …ìural Amen, ko …ìernde makko dee∆¥ira. Sulaymaana mo∆¥∆¥ii jeyaa…óo. Ko o …óuu…óunoo…óo tuubugol ruttoo e Allah."
  38,31,"Janto nde o hollanoo kiikii…óeere, pucci yoo…óu…ói yaawu…ói, daroray…ói taape tati, …ìamta naya…ìal ngal. ∆Åe seeraali e hollugol mo …óum, haa naange muti."
  38,32,"Sulaymaana maaki: Mi …ìurnorii yi…ógol jawdi, wano …óii pucci, e dow ko mi jantotoo Joomi am kon, haa naange ngen mutoyii, mi fa…óii julde alansaraa nden."
  38,33,"Ruttee lam …óii pucci. ∆Åe rutti mo …ói, o woni e sodirgol …ói kaafa, ka taape(koyde) e ka daa…óe majji."
  38,34,"Gom…óii Men jarribike Sulaymaana, Men werii e jullere makko laamu nden, seytaniiru, nannditiniindu e ne…ó…óo, ndu ardii see…óa e laamu makko ngun. Refti Sulaymaana hettiti laamu makko ngun, o wuurti mbo e seytaniiru ndun."
  38,35,"Sulaymaana maaki: Joomi am, haforanam goopi am, ye…óaa lam laamu heeranii ngu lam, ngu haananaa go…ó…óo goo, …ìaawo am. Ko An Joomi, woni …óuu…óugol mawni dokke."
  38,36,"Men jaabinani mo toraare nden. Men eltani mo henndu ndun, tawi ndu wifiray neweende, e yamiroore makko, e hoore doole e yaawere mayru fow, ndu na…ìa mo ka o faalaa."
  38,37,"Men eltani mo kadi seytanuuji …óin, …ói woni e ley konngol makko. No e majji mahaynoo…ói, go…ó…ói …óin mutaynoo…ói ka maayo, …ói yaltina ka≈ã≈ãe."
  38,38,"Seytanuuji goo, ko rawaniyanke, eltanaa…ói mo. ∆äin ko dummbaa…ói e jolokooje, ka …ói waawaa memminaade."
  38,39,"∆äum ko ko Men ye…óu maa, an Sulaymaana, ka jaabingol toraare maa. Okku mo yi…óan…óaa, maa …óalaa mo faala…óaa. A lamnditortaake go…ó…óum e mun."
  38,40,"Pellet, Sulaymaana ka Amen, ko jeyaa…óo e …ìadnaa…ìe, maranaa…ìe ruttorde mo∆¥∆¥unde, woni Aljanna."
  38,41,"Janto kadi, an Nulaa…óo, jeyaa…óo Amen on Ayyuuba, nde o torinoo Allah Joomi makko, wonnde: Seytaane memirii lam tampere lebtatnde."
  38,42,"Men wi'ani mo: latir tunndawal(koyngal) maa ka leydi. O wa…ói …óum, …ìunndu …ìullitanii mo …óon: tawi go…ó…óam …óam, ko yaretee …óam, o lootora …óama, ko o ittira lorra e tampere memunoonde mo nden."
  38,43,"Men jaabinani mo toraare. Men huncani mo lorra makko kan, Men ye…ói mo …ìeynguure makko nden, Men …ìeydani mo ge…óal…ìe e taaniraa…ìe yeru ma…ì…ìe, yurmeende immorde e Amen, e njo…ìdi mu√±al makko ngal, e fii no joomiraa…ìe haqqille hisu…óe …ìen, waajitora, wonnde mu√±al, adday hoyeende e warjeede."
  38,44,"Nde Annabi Ayyuuba tikkannoo debbo makko on, o woondiri piyugol mo loyru teemedere. Men wi'ani mo ontuma : Ko an Ayyuuba, nanngiri sookewo maa ngon, tamannde hu…óo, piyiraa mo …óum, no hunniraa woodoore maa nden, hara a firtaa nden. O wa…ói …óum. Men tawu mo, ko o mu√±√±ii…óo e ko Men jarribori mo kon. O mo∆¥∆¥ii jeyaa…óo. Pellet, ko o …óuu…óunoo…óo tuubugol ruttoo ka Allah."
  38,45,"Janto kadi, an Nulaa…óo, jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen …ìe Men su…ìii, e Nulaa…ìe Amen, …ìe Men immini: Ibraahiima, e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba. ∆Åe laatino joomiraa…ìe cemmbe ka …óoftagol Allah, …óa…ì…ìa welayee Makko. ∆Åe woni kadi joomiraa…ìe gii…óe, ja…ìoo…ìe goonga."
  38,46,"Men heertinanii heertinannde, nden woni wuurnugol …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, anntidugol fii galle laakara …óen, hebilarona…óe, golle mo∆¥∆¥e, nodda yim…ìe …ìen e mum."
  38,47,"Kadi, …ìee ka Amen, ko jeyaa…ìe e su…ìiraa…ìe …óoftagol dewgol Men, su…ìiraa…ìe tammbitagol Nulal Amen ngal, yottina e yim…ìe …ìen."
  38,48,"Janto kadi, an Annabiijo, Ismaa'iila ge…óal Ibraahiima, e Ysa'u, e Zal-Kifli, mantiraa…ìe mantoore labaande, tawde hi…ìe hanndi e mun. Kala e ma…ì…ìe, ko jeyaa…ìe e su…ìaa…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen ka Allah."
  38,49,"∆äum ko annditirgol …ìee, mantoore labaande, ka Alqur'aana. Ko pellet, hino woodani hulir…ìe Allah …ìen …óoftagol Mo wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, ruttorde mo∆¥∆¥unde, ka galle laakara."
  38,50,"Nden ruttorde mo∆¥∆¥unde, ko Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal, …ói …ìe naatoyta √ëalnde Darngal, hara dame majji no udditiranaa…ìe, sa…ónugol …ìe."
  38,51,"Hara ko …ìe so…ì…ìindii…ìe e hoore dan…óe cu…óinanaa…óe …ìe, hi…ìe nodda golloo…ìe ton …ìen, lamndoo…ìe muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói serti, e noone kala e njaram, mo …ìe yi…ói, wano sanngara ekw."
  38,52,"Hino woodani …ìe ton: rew…ìe ra…ì…ìinay…ìe ndaar…óe mun e wor…ìe mun tun, fot…ìe e duu…ìi."
  38,53,"Ko …óum woni ko foda…óon e njo…ìdi laa…ìundi, onon gom…óu…ìe …ìen, √ëalnde Darngal. Fii golle mon mo∆¥∆¥e …óen aduna."
  38,54,"Pellet, njo…ìdi jantaandi fii mun ndin …óoo, ko arsike Amen, mo Men arsikoyta gom…óu…ìe …ìen, √ëalnde Darngal. Arsike duumotoo…óo, mo ta∆¥ondirtaa, o lannataa."
  38,55,"Ko jantoo kon, ko njo…ìdi gom…óu…ìe …ìen. Pellet, hino woodani kadi yawtir…ìe keeri Allah …óin geddi e keeferaaku, njo…ìdi sertundi; kam…ìe on, ko ruttorde …ìurnde bonnde woodani …ìe √ëalnde Darngal."
  38,56,"Njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, ko Jahannama, huu…ìitaynge …ìe, nge tampina …ìe nguleeki e ooyeende. Hi…ìe mari ton nda…ó…óu…óe, kono …óe bonii da…ó…óu…óe!"
  38,57,"∆äen lepte, ko ndiyam ha…ótu…óam e fatugol, e mbor- di ilatndi e …ìalli yim…ìe leptetee…ìe …ìen ka Yiite. Yo …ìe sulko …óam, sabu ko njaram ma…ì…ìe …óam ittataa …óonka …óan non!"
  38,58,"Hino woodani …ìe lepte goo, nanndu…óe e majje. ∆äen ko nooneeji, …ói …ìe leptiroytee ka laakara."
  38,59,"Si yim…ìe Yiite …ìen naatoyii e magge, …ìe ukkondi- royii hakkunde ma…ì…ìe e weljugol hoynindira, kala e ma…ì…ìe wona e da…óndinagol e oya. Wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe wi'i: E hino fedde naatidoyay nde e mon ka Yiite. ∆Åe jaaboo …ìe: Toolii alanaa …ìe, tawde ko …ìe mee…óiray…ìe Yiite ngen, no men mee…óirta nge."
  38,60,"Fedde jokkunoo…ìe …ìeya …ìen wi'ana koohoo…ìe …ìen: ko onon …ìee koohoo…ìe kan, woni toolii alanaa, ko onon defi men …óee lepte muusu…óe, sabu ko mojjinir…óon men kon, bewin…óon men. Ndee √±ii…ìirde Jahannama …óoo, nde bonii √±ii…ìirde naatoo…ìe nge fow."
  38,61,"∆Åe wi'a kadi: Joomi amen, defu…óo men majjugol on, …ìaawo nde peewal ngal ari e amen, sowan mo lepte …óen ka Yiite."
  38,62,"Bew…ìe townitii…ìe …ìen wi'a: Ko ha…ói men yi'ugol ka Yiite gaa, wor…ìe …ìe men limtaynoo ka aduna, jeyaa…ìe e bom…ìe, hanndu…ìe e lepte?"
  38,63,"Hara men falju e kon men jagitornoo …ìe kon jalnori, tawa …ìe handaa e lepte, kaa hara …ìe naatu Yiite, gite amen yawti …ìe?"
  38,64,"Pellet, ko Men jantanii on kon, e ko yeddu…ìe …ìen wenjorndirta hakkunde ma…ì…ìe √ëalnde Darngal, ko goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un."
  38,65,"An Muhammadu, maakan yim…ìe maa yeddu…ìe …ìen: Anndee ko mi jertinoowo on, e lepte Allah …óen, fii wata …óe yanir e mon, sabu yeddugol mon fenna Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Anndo kadi, alaa rewetee…óo hanndu…óo e dewal, si wanaa Allah Senii…óo On. Ko Kanko woni Bajjo ka mawngu e sifaaji e ka in…óe Mun, Foolu…óo kala huunde. Mo huunde kala yankinii ∆äum."
  38,66,"Ko Kanko woni Jey…óo kammuuli …óin, e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde majji. Foolu…óo e laamu Mun, Mo gooto foolataa. Haforoowo junuubi jeyaa…ìe Makko tuubu…ìe …ìen."
  38,67,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee fennoo…ìe : ndee Alqur'aanaare, ko kumpital mawngal fiyaaku."
  38,68,"Kono hi…óon …óuurnii e on kabaaru mawnu…óo fiyaaku. On alaa ye∆¥∆¥itaade e makko."
  38,69,"Mi he…ìataano ganndal, e ko fe∆¥∆¥aynoo hakkunde Malaa'ika'en, fii tagugol Aadama, si wanaano Allah wahayini …óum e am, O anndimmi."
  38,70,"Allah wahayiniraali e am, si wanaa tawde ko mi jertinoowo on, e lepte Makko …óen, …ìanninano on."
  38,71,"Janto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: Min ko Mi tagiroowo …ìanndinke, woni Aadama (yo o his) immorde e loopal."
  38,72,"Si Mi fotindirii tagu makko ngun, Mi mo∆¥∆¥intinii mbaadi makko ndin, mi wuttii ruuhu Am on e makko, ko yo on sujjan mo."
  38,73,"Malaa'ika'en …óoftii yamaruyee Joomi ma…ì…ìe on, …ìe sujji …ìe denndaangal, sujuudu teddungal. Alaa mo sujjanaano Aadama e ma…ì…ìe."
  38,74,"Si wanaa Ibuliisa, o mawnitinii sujjugol ngol, o woni jeyaa…óo e yeddu…ìe Joomi mun."
  38,75,"Allah daali: Ko an yo Ibuliisa, ko hon…óum ha…óu maa sujjangol Aadama, mo tagirmi juu…óe Am? Ko mawnintinaare ha…óu maa kaa hari nun ko a jeyanoo…óo e townitanii…ìe Joomi mun …ìen?"
  38,76,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Ko min …ìuri Aadama mo∆¥∆¥ude. Tawde A tagirii lam immorde e yiite, A tagirii mo kanko e loopal. Sikkugol mo wonnde yiite …ìuri loope teddude."
  38,77,"Alla daalani ibuliisa: Yaltu ka Aljanna ton, sabu ko a hu…óaa…óo Kiitaa…óa."
  38,78,"Pellet, ra…óeede ka Aljanna fawike ma, haa √ëalaande n…ìjodi kuu…óe, nden woni √ëalnde Darngal."
  38,79,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Nennitanam maayugol, haa √±alnde immintaa jeyaa…ìe Maa …ìen."
  38,80,"Allah daali: A jeyaama e nennitanaa…ìe …ìen."
  38,81,"A nennitanaama, haa e happu anndaa…óo, halkeede ma."
  38,82,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Mi woondirii kattal e mawngu Maa ngun ! Ma mi majjin …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama …ìen fow."
  38,83,"Si wanaa …ìen …ìe da…óndu-∆äaa bone am, heertinir-∆äaa …ìe e rewugol Am tun."
  38,84,"Allah daali: goonga kan ko e Am, ko goonga Mi wowlata, wanaa ko lunndi …óum."
  38,85,"Ma Mi hebbinire Jahannama √ëande Darngal, an e …ìen jokku…ìe ma, yeddu…ìe …ìen e banii Aadama …ìen fow."
  38,86,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan sirkoo…ìe …ìen: Mi lamndaaki on e ko mi yottinta e mon kon, njo…ìdi. Mi wonaali kadi etotoo…óo sincugol …ìeyda e ko mi yamiraa kon."
  38,87,"Alqur'aana wonaali, si wanaa waaju, wonannde hellifaa…ìe yim…ìe e jinna …ìen."
  38,88,"Ma on anndu kabaaru ndee Alqur'aanaare, wonnde ko nde goonga, …ìaawo dummunna …ìadii…óo, tuma nde maayoton."
